data.description: 4/3/2 pool home with a flex room on a corner lot. Built in 2021, this home features an open concept kitchen, living and dining area with Moen wood flooring, 10 ft ceilings and a split bedroom floor plan. The open kitchen has plenty of cabinets and easy access to the backyard entertainment area. The backyard features wooden decking off the rear of the home with a fire pit and built in seating along with a custom built tiki bar and picnic area, above ground pool, lush landscaping, garden and a new 10x20 ($10,000) shed. The back yard is fenced and offers plenty of privacy and perfect for entertaining. Centrally located to shopping, dining, parks/dog park and easy driving to the beach.
